This repository redistributes third-party robot models and assets that remain
under their own licenses. Each vendored asset keeps its original LICENSE file in
its assets/<asset>/ directory, and THIRD_PARTY_LICENSES.md lists every asset with
its license and origin. Those third-party licenses (e.g. BSD-3-Clause, MIT,
CC-BY-4.0) govern the corresponding asset files, not this repository's Apache-2.0
license.

No assets from NVIDIA Isaac Sim / Omniverse Nucleus are included or derived from;
robot models are sourced from their upstream URDF/MJCF descriptions and converted
to USD locally.
